c1c5a9aa73ac24a02b09422802796821fc46fd43.commit.message:
Removed the two-argument constructor from GroupPrincipal and its associated "wiki" field. This interacted in a very subtle way with LocalPolicy to prevent GroupPrincipal privilege grants from being processed correctly. We concluded that this "feature", while intended to be used with multi-wiki environments, was fatally broken from the start. Also: many, many little fixes to remove Checkstyle issues.
